hadiths[89]{hadithnumber,text}:
7137,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne meri itaat ki us ne Allah ki itaat ki aur jisne meri nafarmani ki us ne Allah ki nafarmani ki aur jisne mere (muqarrar kiye huey) ameer ki itaat ki us ne meri itaat ki aur jisne mere ameer ki nafarmani ki us ne meri nafarmani ki.''
7138,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aagaah ho jao tum mein se har aik nigahbaan hai aur har aik se uski riaya ke barey mein sawal kya jaeyga to imam ( ameerul-momineen ( logon par nigahbaan hai aur us se uski riaya ke barey mein sawal hoga. mard apne ghar walon ka nigahbaan hai aur us se uski riaya ke barey mein sawal hoga aur aurat apne shauhar ke ghar walon aur uske bachchon ki nigahbaan hai aur us se unke barey mein sawal hoga aur kisi shakhs ka ghulam apne sardaar ke maal ka nigahbaan hai aur us se uske barey mein sawal hoga. aagah ho jao ke tum mein se har aik nigahbaan hai aur har aik se uski riaya ke barey mein poochhgachh hogii.''
7139,"main Quraish ke aik wafad ke sath Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas tha ke unhein malum hua ke Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke an-qareeb qabila qahtaan ka aik badshah hoga. Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) is par ghussa huey aur khadey ho kar Allah ki tareef uski shaan ke mutabiq ki phir farmaya, ammaa ba'd! mujhey malum hua hai ke tum mein se kuchh log aisi hadis bayan kartey hain jo na kitabullah mein hai aur aur na Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se manqul hai, ye tum mein se jaahi log hain. to tum aisey khayalat se bachtey raho jo tumhen gumrah kar dein kyonke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna hai ke ye Amr ( khilafat ( Quraish mein rahega. koi bhi unse agar dushmanii karega to Allah usey ruswa kar dega lekin us waqt tak jab tak wo Deen ko qaaim rakhengey . is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Naeem ne ibne-Mubarak se ki hai, unse Mamar ne, unse Zohri ne aur unse Muhammad-bin Juber ne."
7140,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''ye Amre-khilaafat us waqt tak Quraish mein rahega jab tak unmein 2 log bhi baqi raheingey.''
7141,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''rashk bas 2 aadmiyon par hi kya jana chahiye aik wo shakhs jisey Allah ne maal diya aur phir us ne wo haq ke rastey mein be-daregh kharch kya aur doosra wo shakhs jisey Allah ne hikmate-deen ka ilm (Qur'aan w hadis ka ( diya hai wo uske muwafiq faisley karta hai.''
7142,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' suno aur itaat karo, chahe tum par kisi aisey habshi ghulam ko hi aamil banaya jaey jiska sar munaqqaa ki tarah chhota ho.''"
7143,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne apne ameer mein koi bura kaam dekha to usey sabr karna chahiye kyonke koi agar jamat se aik baalisht bhi juda ho to wo jahiliyat ki maut marega.''
7144,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se farmaya ''musalmaan ke liye ameer ki baat sunnaa aur uski itaat karna zaroori hai, un chizon mein bhi jinhein wo pasand karey aur unmein bhi jinhein wo na-pasand karey, jab tak usey gunah ka hukm na diya jaey. phir jab usey gunah ka hukm diya jaey to na sunnaa baqi rehta hai na itaat karnaa.''"
7145,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik dasta bheja aur is par Ansar ke aik shakhs ko ameer banaya aur logon ko hukm diya ke unki itaat karein. phir ameer fauj ke logon par ghussa huey aur kaha ke kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tumhen meri itaat ka hukm nahi diya hai? logon ne kaha ke zaroor diya hai. is par unhon-ne kaha ke main tumhen hukm deta hun ke lakdi jama karo aur us se aag jalaao aur is mein kood pado . logon ne lakdi jama ki aur aag jalaaii, jab koodnaa chaha to aik doosrey ko log dekhney lagey aur unmein se kuchh ne kaha ke ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki farmaanbardaarii aag se bchney ke liye ki thi, kya phir ham usmein khud hi dakhil ho jaaein. usi doran mein aag thandii ho gaee aur ameer ka ghussa bhi jata raha. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska zikr kya gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar ye log usmein kood padtey to phir usmein se na nikal saktey. itaat sirf achi baton mein hai."
7146,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey Abdur-Rehmaan! hukumat ke taalib na bannaa kyonke agar tumhen maangney ke baad hukumat mili to tum uske hawale kar diye jaogey aur wo tumhen bila maangey mili to usmein tumhari ( Allah ki taraf se) madad ki jaeygi aur agar tum ne qism kha li ho phir iske siwa dusri cheez mein bhalai dekho to apni qism ka kaffara ada kar do aur wo kaam karo jis mein bhalai ho.''
7147,mujh se Abdur-Rehman bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke unse Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey Abdur-Rehman ibne- Samra ! hukumat talab mat karna kyonke agar tumhen maangney ke baad ameerii mili to tum iske hawale kar diye jaogey aur agar tumhen maangey baghair mili to usmein tumhari madad ki jaeygi aur agar tum kisi baat par qism kha lo aur phir iske siwa dusri cheez mein bhalai dekho to wo karo jis mein bhalai ho aur apni qism ka kaffara ada kar do.''
7148,"ham se Ahmed bin Yunus ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha ham se ibne-abi-Ze-ib ne bayan kya, unse Saeed Maqbari ne bayan kya aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum hukumat ka laalach karogey aur ye qiyamat ke din tumharey liye baais nadaamat hogi. to kya hi behtar hai doodh pilaaney wali aur kya hi buri hai doodh chhudaaney waali.''aur Muhammad-bin Bishr ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Abdullah-bin Humran ne bayan kya, kaha ham se abdul-hameed ne bayan kya, unse Saeed al-maqbarii ne, unse Umar-bin hakam ne aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna qaul (mauqoofan) naql kya."
7149,main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat main apni qaum ke 2 aadmiyon ko lekar hazir hua. unmein se aik ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! hamein kahin ka Hakim bana dijiye aur doosrey ne bhi yahi khahish zahir ki. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ham aisey shakhs ko ye zimme-dari nahi saunptey jo usey talab karey aur na usey detey hain jo uska laalachii ho.
7150,"Ubaidullaah-bin-Ziyaad , Ma'qil-bin-Yasaar (Raziallahu anhu) ki iyaadat ke liye us marz mein aaey jis mein unka intiqal hua to Ma'qil-bin-Yasaar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha ke main tumhen aik hadis sunata hun jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha '' jab Allah Taala kisi bande ko kisi raiyat ka Hakim banata hai aur wo khair-khahi ke sath uski hifazat nahi karta to wo jannat ki khushbu bhi nahi paaeyga.''"
7151,ham Ma'qil-bin-Yasaar (Raziallahu anhu) ki iyaadat ke liye unke paas gaey phir Ubaidullah bhi aaey to Maaqil (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha ke main tum se aik aisi hadis bayan karta hun jisey maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar koi shakhs musalmanon ka Hakim banaya gaya aur usne unke maamle mein khayanat ki aur usi haalat mein mar gaya to Allah Taala is par jannat ko haram kar deta hai.
7152,"main Safwan aur Jundub aur unke sathiyon ke paas maujood tha. Safwan apne sathiyon (shaagirdon) ko wasiiyat kar rahe they, phir (safwaan aur unke sathiyon ne Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se) puchha : kya aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kuchh suna hai? unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye kehtey suna hai ke jo logon ko riyaakaarii ke taur par dikhaaney ke liye kaam karega Allah qiyamat ke din uski riyaakaarii ka haal logon ko suna dega aur farmaya ke jo logon ko takleef mein mubtala karega Allah Taala qiyamat ke din usey takleef mein mubtala karega, phir un logon ne kaha ke hamein koi wasiiyat keejiye. unhon-ne kaha ke sabse pahley insan ke jism mein iska pet sadta hai to jo koi taqat rakhta ho ke paak w taiyeb ke siwa aur kuchh na khaaey to usey aisa hi karna chahiye aur jo koi taqat rakhta ho wo chullu bhar khoon baha kar (yani nahaq khoon karke) apne aapko jannat mein janey se rokey. Jurairi kehtey hain ke maine abu-Adbullah se poochha, kon sahib is hadis mein ye kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sunaa? kya Jundub kehtey hain? unhon-ne kaha ke haan, wahi kehtey hain."
7153,"main aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid se nikal rahe they ke aik shakhs masjid ki chaukhat par aa kar ham se mila aur malum kya : ya Rasulullah! qiyamat Kab hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum ne qiyamat ke liye kya taiyaarii ki hai?'' is par wo shakhs khamosh sa ho gaya, phir usne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! maine bahut zyada rozey , Namaz aur sadqa qiyamat ke liye nahi taiyaar kiye hain lekin main Allah aur uske rasool se mohabbat rakhta hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum uske sath hogey jis se tum mohabbat rakhtey ho.''"
7154,"wo apne ghar ki aik aurat se keh rahe they fulaanii ko pahchaantii ho? unhon-ne kaha ke haan. batlaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske paas se guzrey aur wo aik qabr ke paas ro rahi thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah se dar aur sabr kar. us aurat ne jawab diya. aap mere paas se chaley jao, meri museebat aap par nahi padi hai. bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan se hat gaey aur chaley gaey. phir aik sahib udhar se guzrey aur unse puchha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tum se kya kaha tha? us aurat ne kaha ke maine unhein pehchaana nahi. un sahib ne kaha ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) they. phir wo aurat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui. unhon-ne aap ke yahan koi darbaan nahi paya phir arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! maine aapko pehchaana nahi ( tha) . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke sabr to sadma ke shuru mein hi hota hai."
7155,Qais-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath is tarah rahtey they jaisey ameer ke sath kotwaal rehta hai.
7156,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein bheja tha aur unke sath Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi bheja tha.
7157,"aik shakhs Islam laya phir Yahudi ho gaya phir Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur wo shakhs abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas tha. unhon-ne puchha iska kya mamla hai? abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya ke Islam laya phir Yahudi ho gaya, phir unhon-ne kaha ke jab tak main usey qatl na kar loon nahi baithoonga, ye Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka faisla hai."
7158,Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne ladkey (Ubaidullaah) ko likha aur wo us waqt sajistaan mein they ke 2 aadmiyon ke darmyan faisla us waqt na karna jab tum ghusse mein ho kyonke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai ke koi saalis 2 aadmiyon ke darmyan faisla us waqt na karey jab wo ghusse mein ho.
7159,"aik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah! main Allah ki qism subah ki jamat mein falan (Imam Muaz-bin-Jabal ya Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu)) ki wjah se shirkat nahi kar paata kyonke wo hamarey sath is Namaz ko bahut lambi kar detey hain. Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko waz (nasihat) w nasihat ke waqt us se zyada ghazab naak hota kabhi nahi dekha jaisa ke aap us din they. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey logo ! tum mein se kuchh namaziyon ko nafrat dilaane waley hain, to tum mein se jo shakhs bhi logon ko Namaz padhaaey usey ikhtisar karna chahiye kyonke jamat mein boodhey, bachchey aur zarurat mand sab hi hotey hain.''"
7160,"unhon-ne apni biwi ko jabke wo haalate-haiz mein thin (aamna binte-ghifaar) talaaq de di, phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne iska tazkira Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya to aap bahut khafa huey phir farmaya '' unhein chahiye ke wo rujoo kar lein aur unhein apne paas rakhein , yahan tak ke jab wo paak ho jayen phir haaiza hon aur phir paak hon tab agar chahey to usey talaaq de-dey. ''"
7161,"Hind binte- Utba-bin- Rabee aaein aur kaha : ya Rasulullah ! poori zameen ka koi gharaana aisa nahi tha jiske mutaalliq is darje main zillat ki khaahishmand hun jitna aap ke gharaane ki zillat w ruswai ki main khaahishmand thi lekin ab mera ye haal hai ke main sabse zyada khaahishmand hun ke poori zameen ke tamam gharaanon mein aap ka gharaana izzat w sarbulandi wala ho. phir unhon-ne kaha ke Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) kanjoos aadmi hain, to kya mere liye koi harj hai agar main unke maal mein se (unki ijazat ke baghair lekar ( apne ahal w ayaal ko khilaaun? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke tumharey liye koi harj nahi hai, agar tum unhein dastoor ke mutabiq khilaao."
7162,jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ahale-Rome (mojooda Itly) ko khat likhnaa chaha to sahaba ne kaha ke roomii sirf mehar laga hua khat hi qabool kartey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chandi ki aik mehar banwaai maano main uski chamak ko is waqt bhi dekh raha hun aur is par kalima (Muhammad rasoolullah.) naqsh tha.
7163,"wo umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas unke zamaanae-khilaafat mein aaey to unse umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha : kya mujh se ye jo kaha gaya hai wo sahi hai ke tumhen logon ke kaam sipurd kiye jatey hain aur jab uski tankhwaah di jati hai to tum usey lena pasand nahi kartey? maine kaha ke ye sahi hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke tumhara us se maqsad kya hai? maine arz kya ke mere paas ghodey aur ghulam hain aur main khush'haal hun aur main chahta hun ke meri tankhwaah musalmanon par sadqa ho jaey. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke aisa na karo kyonke maine bhi iska irada kya tha jiska tum ne irada kya hai Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey ata kartey they, to main arz kar deta tha ke usey mujh se zyada iske zarurat mand ko ata farma dijiye. aakhir aap ne aik martaba mujhey maal ata kya aur maine wahi baat dohraaii ke usey aisey shakhs ko de dijiye jo iska mujh se zyada zarurat mand ho to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey lo aur uske Malik banney ke baad iska sadqa karo. ye maal jab tumhen is tarah miley ke tum iske na khaahishmand ho aur na usey maanga to usey ley liya karo aur agar is tarah na miley to iske peechhey na padaa karo."
7164,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey ata kartey they, to main kehta ke aap usey de dein jo iska mujh se zyada zarurat mand ho, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey aik martaba maal diya aur maine kaha ke aap usey aisey shakhs ko de dein jo iska mujh se zyada zarurat mand ho to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey ley lo aur uske Malik banney ke baad iska sadqa kar do. ye maal jab tumhen is tarah miley ke tum iske khaahishmand na ho aur na usey tum ne maanga ho to usey ley liya karo aur jo is tarah na miley iske peechhey na padaa karo."
7165,"maine 2 liaan karne walon ko dekha, mein us waqt pandarah saal ka tha aur un donon ke darmyan judai kara di gaee thi."
7166,"qabila Ansar ka aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur arz kya aap ka is barey mein kya khayal hai agar koi mard apni biwi ke sath doosrey mard ko dekhey , kya usey qatl kar sakta hai? phir donon ( miyan biwi ( mein meri maujoodgii mein liaan karaya gaya."
7167,"aik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein they aur unhon-ne aapko awaz di aur kaha : ya Rasulullah ! maine zina kar liya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse munh mod liya lekin jab us ne apne hi khilaf char martaba gawahi di to aap ne us se puchha kya tum paagal ho? usne kaha ke nahi, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein ley jao aur rajm (sangsaar) kar do."
7168,"mein bhi un logon mein tha jinhoney us shakhs ko eidgaah par rajm (sangsaar) kya tha. uski riwayat Younus, Mamar aur ibne-Juraij ne Zohri se ki, unse abu-Salma ne, unse Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se rajm (sangsaar) ke silsiley mein yahi hadis zikr ki."
7169,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' bila shubah mein aik insan hun, tum mere paas apne jhagdey latey ho mumkin hai tum mein se kuchh apne muqaddima ko pesh karne mein doosrey fareeq ke muqable mein zyada charb-zabaan ho aur main tumhari baat sun kar faisla kar dun to jis shakhs ke liye main iske bhai (fareeq mukhaalif) ka koi haq dila dun, chahiye ke wo usey na ley kyonke ye aag ka aik tukda hai jo main usey deta hun."
7170,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hunain ki jang ke din farmaya ''jiske paas kisi maqtool ke barey mein jisey usne qatl kya ho gawahi ho to uska saman usey milega. chunanche main maqtool ke liye gawah talash karne ke liye khada hua to maine kisi ko nahi dekha jo mere liye gawahi de sakey, isliye main baith gaya. phir mere samney aik sura aai aur maine iska zikr Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya to wahan baithey huey aik sahib ne kaha ke is maqtool ka saman jiska abu-Qatada zikr kar rahe hain, mere paas hai. unhein uske liye razi kar dijiye (ke wo ye hathiyar wghaira mujhey de dein) is par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke hargiz nahi. Allah ke sheron mein se aik sher ko nazar andaz karke jo Allah aur uske rasool ki taraf se jang karta hai wo Quraish ke maamooli aadmi ko hathiyar nahi dengey. bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya aur unhon-ne hathiyar mujhey de diye aur maine us se aik baagh khareedaa. ye pahlaa maal tha jo maine (Islam ke baad) hasil kya tha. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha aur mujh se Abdullah-bin Saleh ne bayan kya, unse Lais-bin-Sad ne ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur mujhey wo saman dila diya, aur ahale-hijaaz, Imam Malik wghaira ne kaha ke Hakim ko sirf apne ilm ki buniyad par faisla karna durust nahi. chahe wo maamle par qaza (judge) ka ohda hasil honey ke baad gawah hua ho ya us se pahley aur agar kisi fareeq ne iske samney doosrey ke liye majlis qaza mein kisi haq ka iqrar kya to kuchh logon ka khayal hai ke us buniyad par wo faisla nahi karega balke 2 gawaahon ko bula kar unke samney iqrar karaaega aur kuchh Iraq walon ne kaha hai ke jo kuchh qazi ne adaalat mein dekha ya suna iske mutabiq faisla karega lekin jo kuchh adaalat ke bahar hoga uski buniyad par 2 gawaahon ke baghair faisla nahi kar sakta aur unhiin mein se doosrey logon ne kaha ke uski buniyad par bhi faisla kar sakta hai kyonke wo amanat daar hai. shahadat ka maqsad to sirf haq ka jaanna hai. to qazi ka zaatii ilm gawahi se badh kar hai. aur kuchh unmein se kehtey hain ke amwaal ke barey main to apne ilm ki buniyad par faisla karega aur uske siwa nahi karega aur Qasim ne kaha ke Hakim ke liye durust nahi ke wo koi faisla sirf apne ilm ki buniyad par karey aur doosrey ke ilm ko nazar andaz kar de. haalaanki qazi ka ilm doosrey ki gawahi se badh kar hai lekin chunkey aam musalmanon ki nazar mein is sura mein qazi par tohmat ke aaney ka khatrah hai aur musalmanon ko is tarah bad-gumaanii mein mubtala karna hai aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bad-gumaanii ko na-pasand kya tha aur farmaya tha ke ye Safiya meri biwi hain."
7171,"Safiya-binte-Huyi (Raziallahu anhu)) raat ke waqt) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaein (aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein motakif they) jab wo wapas aaney lagiin to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi unke sath aaey. us waqt 2 Ansari sahabi idhar se guzrey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein bulaya aur farmaya ke ye Safiya hain. un donon ansaariyon ne kaha, Subhan-Allah (kya ham aap par shuba karengey) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke shaitan insan ke andar is tarah daudta hai jaisey khoon daudta hai. uski riwayat Shuaib, ibne-musaafir, ibne-abii ateeq aur Ishaq bin Yahya ne Zohri se ki hai, unse Ali-bin Husain ne aur unse Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi waqia naql kya hai."
7172,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere walid ( abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) (aur Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yaman bheja aur unse farmaya ke aasani paida karna aur tangi na karna aur khushkhabri dena aur nafrat na dilaanaa aur aapas mein ittifaq rakhna. abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha ke hamarey mulk mein shehad ka nabeez ( tubba' ( banaya jata hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke har nasha aawar cheez haram hai. Nazar-bin-Shumail , Abu-Dawud tiyaalisii, Yazeed bin Harun aur Wakee ne Shoba se bayan kya, unse Saeed ne, unse unke walid ne, unse unke dada ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi hadis naql ki."
7173,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qaidiyon ko chhudaao aur dawat karne waley ki dawat qabool karo.''
7174,"bani Asad ke aik shakhs ko sadqe ki wsoolii ke liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tahseeldaar banaya, unka naam ibne-Lutbiiya tha. jab wo lot kar aaey to unhon-ne kaha ke ye aap logon ka hai aur ye mujhey hadiye mein diya gaya hai. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par khadey huey, Sufiyan hi ne ye riwayat bhi ki ke '' phir aap member par chadhey '' phir Allah ki hamd w sana bayan ki aur farmaya ke us aamil ka kya haal hoga jisey ham tehseel ke liye bhejtey hain phir wo aata hai aur kehta hai ke ye maal tumhara hai aur ye mera hai. kyon na wo apne bap ya maa ke ghar betha raha aur dekha hota ke usey hadiya diya jata hai ya nahi. us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, aamil jo cheez bhi (hadiye ke taur par) lega usey qiyamat ke din apni gardan par uthaey huey aayega . agar oont hoga to wo apni awaz nikaaltaa aayega, agar gaaey hogi to wo apni awaz nikaaltii aaeygii, bakri hogi to wo boltii aaeygii, phir aap ne apne hath uthaaey. yahan tak ke ham ne aap ke donon baghlon ki safedi dekhi aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine pahuncha diyaa! teen martaba yahi farmaya, Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne bayan kya ke ye hadis ham se Zohri ne bayan ki aur Hisham ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unse abu-Humed (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke mere donon kanon ne suna aur donon aankhon ne dekha aur Zaid-bin-Saabit sahabi (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi poochh kyonke unhon-ne bhi ye hadis mere sath suni hai. Sufiyan ne kaha Zohri ne ye lafz nahi kaha ke mere kanon ne suna. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha hadis main (khwaar) ka lafz hai yani gaaey ki awaz ya (jawaaz) ka lafz jo lafz ( تجأرون ( se nikla hai jo sura mominoon mein hai yani gaaey ki awaz nikaaltey hongey."
7175,"abu-Huzaifa (Raziallahu anhu) ke) aazad karda ghulam ( Salim , muhaajire-awwaleen ki aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke doosrey sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) masjide-Qubaa mein imamat kya kartey they. un ashaab mein Abu-Bakar , umr , abu-Salma , Zaid aur Aamir-bin-Rabee'a (Raziallahu anhu) bhi hotey they."
7176,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne, jab musalmanon ne qabila Hawazin ke qaidiyon ko ijazat di to farmaya ke mujhey nahi malum ke tum mein se kis ne ijazat di hai aur kis ne nahi di hai. to wapas jao aur tumhara mamla hamarey paas tumharey naqeeb ya chaudhrii aur tumharey sardaar laaein. chunanche log wapas chaley gaey aur unke zimme-daaron ne unse baat ki aur phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aa kar itlaa di ke logon ne dilii khushi se ijazat de di hai."
7177,"rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne, jab musalmanon ne qabila Hawazin ke qaidiyon ko ijazat di to farmaya ke mujhey nahi malum ke tum mein se kis ne ijazat di hai aur kis ne nahi di hai. to wapas jao aur tumhara mamla hamarey paas tumharey naqeeb ya chaudhrii aur tumharey sardaar laaein. chunanche log wapas chaley gaey aur unke zimme-daaron ne unse baat ki aur phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aa kar itlaa di ke logon ne dilii khushi se ijazat de di hai."
7178,ham apne haakimon ke paas jatey hain aur unke haq mein wo baatein kehtey hain ke bahar aaney ke baad ham iske khilaf kehtey hain. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ham isey nifaq kehtey they.
7179,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke badtareen wo shakhs do-rukha hai, kisi ke samney iska aik rukh hota hai aur doosrey ke samney doosra rukh barat'taa hai."
7180,Hind ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke (unke shauhar ( Abu-Sufiyan kanjoos hain aur mujhey unke maal mein se leney ki zarurat hoti hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke dastoor ke mutabiq itna ley liya karo jo tumharey aur tumharey bachchon ke liye kafi ho.
7181,"unhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne khabar di. aap ne apne hujre ke darwazey par jhagdey ki awaz suni to bahar unki taraf nikley. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main bhi aik insan hun aur mere paas log muqaddmey lekar aatey hain. mumkin hai unmein se aik fareeq doosrey fareeq se bolney mein zyada umda ho aur main yaqin kar loon ki wahi sachcha hai aur is tarah iske muwafiq faisla kar dun. to jis shakhs ke liye bhi main kisi musalman ka haq dila dun to wo jahannam ka aik tukda hai wo chahey usey ley ya chhod de, mein usko dar-haqiqat dozakh ka aik tukda dila raha hun."
7182,"Utba-bin- abii-waqaas ne apne bhai Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye wasiiyat ki thi ke Zam-aa ki londi (ka ladka ( mera hai. tum usey apni parwarish mein ley lenaa. chunanche fateh Makka ke din Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey ley liya aur kaha ke ye mere bhai ka ladka hai aur mujhey iske barey mein unhon-ne wasiiyat ki thi, phir abd-bin-Zam'a khadey huey aur kaha ke ye mera bhai , mere walid ki londi ka ladka hai aur unhiin ke faraash par paida hua. chunanche ye donon Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas pahunchey. Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! mere bhai ka ladka hai, unhon-ne mujhey uski wasiiyat ki thi aur abd-bin-Zam'a ne kaha ke mera bhai hai, mere walid ki londi ka ladka hai aur unhiin ke bistar par paida hua. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke abd-bin-Zam'a ! ye tumhara hai, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bachcha bistar ka hota hai aur zaanii ke liye patthar hai. phir aap ne Sauda-binte-Zama (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke us ladkey se parda kya karo kyonke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ladkey ki Utba se mushabihat (similarity) dekh li thi. chunanche us ne Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ko maut tak nahi dekha."
7183,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo shakhs aisi qism khaaey jo jhooti ho jiske zariey wo kisi doosrey ka maal mar ley to Allah se wo us haal mein mileygaa ke wo is par ghazabnaak hoga.'' phir Allah Taala ne ye aayat (uskii tasdeeq mein) nazil farmai ( إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله‏ وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا ( '' bila shubah jo log Allah ke ahad aur uski qasmon ko thodi poonjii ke badley khareedtey hain''
7184,itney mein Ashas (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aa gaey. abhi Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) unse hadis bayan kar hi rahe they. unhon-ne kaha ke mere hi barey mein ye aayat nazil hui thi aur aik shakhs ke barey mein mera unse kuwein ke barey mein jhagdaa hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( mujh se) kaha ke tumharey paas koi gawahi hai? maine kaha ke nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir fareeq muqabil ki qism par faisla hoga. maine kaha ke phir to ye ( jhooti ( qism kha lega . chunanche aayat ( إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله‏ ( '' bila shubah jo log Allah ke ahad ko '' nazil hui.
7185,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne darwazey par jhagdaa karne walon ki awaz suni aur unki taraf nikley. phir unse farmaya ke main tumharey hi jaisa insan hun, mere paas log muqaddima lekar aatey hain, mumkin hai aik fareeq doosrey se zyada umda bolney wala ho aur main uske liye us haq ka faisla kar dun aur ye samjhoon ke maine faisla sahi kya hai (halanke wo sahi na ho) to jiske liye main kisi musalman ke haq ka faisla kar dun to bila shubah ye faisla jahannam ka aik tukda hai."
7186,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko malum hua ke aap ke sahaba mein se aik ne apne ghulam ko mudabbir bana diya hai (ke unki maut ke baad wo aazad ho jaaeyga) chunkey unke paas iske siwa aur koi maal nahi tha isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us ghulam ko aath (8) so dirham mein bech diya aur uski qeemat unhein bhej di.
7187,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik lashkar bheja aur uska ameer Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ko banaya lekin unki sardaarii par ta'an kya gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke agar aaj tum unki amaarat ko mat'oon qarar detey ho to tum ne us se pahley iske walid (Zaid (Raziallahu anhu)) ki amaarat ko bhi mat'oon qarar diya tha aur Allah ki qism ! wo amaarat ke liye haqdaar they aur wo mujhey tamam logon mein sabse zyada azeez they aur ye (Usaama (Raziallahu anhu)) unke baad sabse zyada mujhey azeez hai.
7188,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah ke nazdeek sabse mabghooz (jis par ghussa aur ghazab ho) wo shakhs hai jo sakht jhagdaaloo ho.''
7189,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Khalid-bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ko banii-Jazeema ki taraf bheja (jab unhein Islam ki dawat di) to wo ( أسلمنا‏) ( ham Islam laey ( keh kar achi tarah izhar Islam na kar sakey balke kehney lagey ke) صبأنا صبأنا ( (ham apne Deen se phir gaey, ham apne Deen se phir gaey ( is par Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) unhein qatl aur qaid karne lagey aur ham mein se har shakhs ko uske hisse ka qaidi diya aur hamein hukm diya ke har shakhs apne qaidi ko qatl kar de. is par maine kaha ke Allah ki qasam! main apne qaidi ko qatl nahi karunga aur na mere sathiyon mein koi apne qaidi ko qatl karega. phir ham ne iska zikr Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey Allah ! main is se Bara't (Tauba) zahir karta hun jo Khalid-bin Waleed ne kya, 2 martaba ."
7190,"qabila bani Amr-bin-Auf mein aapasii ladai ho gaee. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko uski itlaa mili to aap ne Zohar ki Namaz padhi aur unke yahan suleh karaaney ke liye tashrif laey. jab Asr ki Namaz ka waqt hua (Madina mein) to Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne azan di aur iqamat kahi . aap ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko Namaz padhaaney ka hukm diya tha. chunanche wo aagey badhey , itney main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif ley aaey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz hi mein they, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon ki saf ko cheertey huey aagey badhey aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechhey khadey ho gaey aur us saf mein aagey jo unse qareeb thi. Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke logon ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aamad ko bataaney ke liye hath maarey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) jab Namaz shuru kartey to khatm karne se pahley kisi taraf tawajjoh nahi kartey they. jab unhon-ne dekha ke hath par hath maarna ruktaa hi nahi to aap mutwajjeh huey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko apne peechhey dekha lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ishara kya ke Namaz poori karein aur aap ne is tarah hath se apni jagah thahrey rehney ka ishara kya Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) thodi der Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm par Allah ki hamd karne ke liye thahrey rahe, phir aap ultey paon peechhey aa gaey. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye dekha to aap aagey badhey aur logon ko aap ne Namaz padhai. Namaz poori karne ke baad aap ne farmaya, Abu-Bakar ! jab maine irshad kar diya tha to aapko Namaz poori padhaaney mein kya cheez rukawat thi? unhon-ne arz kya, ibne-abii-qahaafa ke liye munasib nahi tha ke wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki imamat karey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke (namaz mein) jab koi mamla pesh aaey to mardon ko Subhan-Allah kehna chahiye aur aurton ko hath par hath maarna chahiye"
7191,"jang yamaama mein kasrat se ( qaari sahaba ki) shahadat ki wjah se Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey bula bhejaa. unke paas umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se kaha ke umr mere paas aaey aur kaha ke jange-yamaama mein Quran ke qaariyon ka qatl bahut hua hai aur mera khayal hai ke dusri jangon mein bhi isi tarah wo Shahid kiye jaeinge aur Quran aksar zaaye ho jaeyga main samajhta hun ke aap Quran Majeed ko (kitaabii sura mein) jama karne ka hukm dein. is par maine umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke main koi aisa kaam kaisey kar sakta hun jisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nahi kya. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Allah ki qasam! ye to kaare-khair hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) is maamle mein barabar mujh se kehtey rahe yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne isi tarah is mamley mein mera bhi Sina khol diya jis tarah umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka tha aur main bhi wahi munasib samajhney laga jisey umr (Raziallahu anhu) munasib samajhtey they. Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke mujh se Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke tum jawan ho, aqlmand ho aur ham tumhen kisi barey mein muttahim bhi nahi samajhtey tum Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wahi bhi likhtey they, to tum us Quran Majeed (ki aayatein ( ko talash karo aur aik jagah jama kar do. Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Allah ki qism ! agar Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) mujhey kisi pahaad ko utha kar dusri jagah rakhney ka mukallaf kartey to uska bojh bhi mein itna na mehsus karta jitna ke mujhey Quran Majeed ko jama karne ke hukm se mehsus hua. maine un logon se kaha ke aap kis tarah aisa kaam kartey hain jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nahi kya Abu-Bakar ne kaha ke Allah ki qasam! ye khair hai. chunanche mujhey aamada karne ki koshish kartey rahe, yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne us kaam ke liye mera bhi Sina khol diya jiske liye Abu-Bakar w umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka Sina khola tha aur main bhi wahi munasib khayal karne laga jisey wo log munasib khayal kar rahe they. chunanche maine Quran Majeed ki talash shuru ki. usey main khajoor ki chhaal, chamdey wghaira ke tukdon, patley patthar ke tukdon aur logon ke seenon se jama karne laga. maine sura Tauba ki aakhiri aayat (لقد جاءكم رسول من أنفسكم) aakhir tak Khuzaima ya abu-Khuzaima (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas paai aur usko sura mein shamil kar liya. (Qur'aan Majeed ke ye murattab) saheefey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas rahe jab tak wo zinda rahey. yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne unhein wafat di phir wo umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aagey aur aakhir waqt tak unke paas rahe. jab aapko bhi Allah Taala ne wafat di to wo Hafsa binte- umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas mehfooz rahe Muhammad-bin Ubaidullah ne kaha ke) اللخاف (ke lafz se theekrii murad hai jisey ( خزف‏ ( kehtey hain."
7192,"ham se Ismail ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Imam Malik ne bayan kya, unse abu-Laila bin-Abdullah-bin Abdur-Rehman bin Sehal ne, unse Sehal bin abi Hasma ne, unhein Sehal aur unki qaum ke kuchh doosrey zimmedaaron ne khabar di ke Abdullah, Sehal aur mahiisa (Raziallahu anhu) khaibar ki taraf (khajoor leney ke liye) gaey. kyonke tang dasti mein mubtala they. phir mahiisa ko bataya gaya ke Abdullah ko kisi ne qatl karke garhey ya kuwein mein daal diya hai. phir wo yahudiyon ke paas gaey aur kaha ke Allah ki qasam! tum ne hi qatl kya hai. unhon-ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! ham ne unhein nahi qatl kya. phir wo wapas aaey aur apni qaum ke paas aaey aur unse zikr kya. iske baad wo aur unke bhai huwesa jo unse badey they aur Abdur-Rehman bin Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) aaey, phir mahiisa (Raziallahu anhu) ne baat karni chahi kyonke aap hi khaibar mein maujood they lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse kaha ke badey ko aagey karo, badey ko aap ki murad umr ki badaai thi. chunanche huwesa ne baat ki, phir mahiisa ne bhi baat ki. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Yahudi tumharey sathi ki diyat ada karein warna ladai ke liye taiyaar ho jaaein. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahudiyon ko us muqaddime mein likha . unhon-ne jawab mein ye likha ke ham ne unhein nahi qatl kya hai. phir aap ne huwesa, mahiisa aur Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke kya aap log qism kha kar apne Shahid sathi ke khoon ke mustahiq ho saktey hain? un logon ne kaha ke nahi (kyonke jurm kartey dekha nahi tha) phir aap ne farmaya, kya aap logon ke bajaey Yahudi qism khaaein (ke unhon-ne qatl nahi kya hai) ? unhon-ne kaha ke wo musalman nahi hain aur wo jhooti qism kha saktey hain. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni taraf se so oonton ki diyat ada ki aur wo oont ghar mein laey gaey. Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke unmein se aik ontni ne mujhey laat maarii."
7193,"aik dehati aaey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! hamara faisla kitabullah ke mutabiq kar dijiye. phir doosrey fareeq khadey huey aur unhon-ne bhi kaha ke ye sahi kehtey hain, hamara faisla kitabullah se kar dijiye. phir dehati ne kaha mera ladka us shakhs ke yahan mazdoor tha, phir us ne uski biwi ke sath zina kar liya to logon ne mujh se kaha ke tumharey ladkey ka hukm usey rajm (sangsaar) karna hai lekin maine apne ladkey ki taraf se so bakriyon aur aik baandi ka fidya de diya. phir maine ahale-ilm se puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke tumharey ladkey ko so kode maarey jaeinge aur aik saal ke liye Shahar badr hoga. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tumharey darmyan Allah ki kitab ke mutabiq faisla karunga . baandi aur bakriyan to tumhen wapas mileingii aur terey ladkey ki saza so kode aur aik saal ke liye jilaa watan hona hai aur Anees (jo aik sahabi they) se farmaya ke tum uski biwi ke paas jao aur usey rajm (sangsaar) karo. chunanche Anees (Raziallahu anhu) uske paas gaey aur usey rajm (sangsaar) kya."
7194,"eik dehati aaey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! hamara faisla kitabullah ke mutabiq kar dijiye. phir doosrey fareeq khadey huey aur unhon-ne bhi kaha ke ye sahi kehtey hain, hamara faisla kitabullah se kar dijiye. phir dehati ne kaha mera ladka us shakhs ke yahan mazdoor tha, phir us ne uski biwi ke sath zina kar liya to logon ne mujh se kaha ke tumharey ladkey ka hukm usey rajm (sangsaar) karna hai lekin maine apne ladkey ki taraf se so bakriyon aur aik baandi ka fidya de diya. phir maine ahale-ilm se puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke tumharey ladkey ko so kode maarey jaeinge aur aik saal ke liye Shahar badr hoga. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tumharey darmyan Allah ki kitab ke mutabiq faisla karunga . baandi aur bakriyan to tumhen wapas mileingii aur terey ladkey ki saza so kode aur aik saal ke liye jilaa watan hona hai aur Anees (jo aik sahabi they) se farmaya ke tum uski biwi ke paas jao aur usey rajm (sangsaar) karo. chunanche Anees (Raziallahu anhu) uske paas gaey aur usey rajm (sangsaar) kya."
7195,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya ke yahudiyon ki tahreer seekhein, yahan tak ke main yahudiyon ke naam Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke khutoot likhtaa tha aur jab Yahudi aapko likhtey to unke khutoot aapko padh kar sunata tha. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abdur-Rehman bin Haatib se poochha, us waqt unke paas Ali, Abdur-Rehman aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bhi maujood they ke ye londi kya kehti hai? Abdur-Rehman bin Haatib ne kaha ke ameerul-momineen ye aapko iske mutaalliq bataatii hai jisne iske sath zina kya hai. (jo yarghoos naam ka ghulam tha) aur abu-Jamra ne kaha ke main Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aur logon ke darmyan tarjamani karta tha aur kuchh logon (Imam Muhammad aur imam Shaafaii) ne kaha ke Hakim ke liye 2 tarjamon ka hona zaroori hai."
7196,"Abu-Sufiyan bin Harab ne unhein khabar di ke Hiraql ne unhein Quraish ki aik jamat ke sath bula bhejaa, phir apne tarjuman se kaha, unse kaho ke main unke barey mein poochhoonga. agar ye mujh se jhoot baat kahey to usey jhutlaa dein. phir poori hadis bayan ki us se kaho ke agar tumhari baatein sahi hain to wo shakhs us mulk ka bhi ho jaeyga jo us waqt mere qadmon ke nichey hai."
7197,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ibne-Lutbiya ko banii-Sulaim ke sadqe ki wsool yaabii ke liye aamil banaya. jab wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ( wsool yaabii karke ( aaey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse hisab talab farmaya to unhon-ne kaha ye to aap logon ka hai aur ye mujhey hadiya diya gaya hai. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir tum apne maan-baap ke ghar kyon na baithey rahe, agar tum sachey ho to wahan bhi tumharey paas hadiya aataa. phir aap khadey huey aur logon ko khutba diya. aap ne hamd w sana ke baad farmaya, ammaa ba'd! main kuchh logon ko kuchh un kaamon ke liye aamil banata hun jo Allah Taala ne mujhey saunpey hain, phir tum mein se koi aik aata hai aur kehta hai ke ye maal tumhara hai aur ye hadiya hai jo mujhey diya gaya hai. agar wo sachcha hai to phir kyon na wo apne bap ya apni maa ke ghar mein betha raha taake wahin uska hadiya pahunch jata. to Allah ki qism ! tum mein se koi agar us maal mein se koi cheez lega . Hisham ne aagey ka mazmoon is tarah bayan kya ke bila haq ke to qiyamat ke din Allah Taala usey is tarah laaeyga ke wo usko uthaey huey hoga. aagah ho jao ke main usey pehchan loonga jo Allah ke paas wo shakhs lekar aayega , oont jo awaz nikal raha hoga ya gaaey jo apni awaz nikal rahi hogi ya bakri jo apni awaz nikal rahi hogi. phir aap ne apne hath uthaey yahan tak ke maine aap ke baghlon ki safedi dekhi aur farmaya kya maine pahuncha diya."
7198,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah ne jab bhi koi Nabi bheja ya kisi ko khaleefa banaya to iske sath 2 rafeeq they aik to unhein neki ke liye kehta aur is par ubhaarta aur doosra unhein burai ke liye kehta aur is par ubhaarta. to masoom wo hai jisey Allah bachaaey rakhey. ''aur Sulaiman-bin Bilal ne is hadis ko Yahya-bin-Saeed Ansari se riwayat kya, kaha mujh ko ibne-Shahab ne khabar di (usko ismaaeelii ne wasl kya) aur ibne-abii ateeq aur Musa-bin-Aqba se bhi, un donon ne ibne-Shahab se yahi hadis (usko Behaqi ne wasl kya) aur Shuaib bin abi Hamza ne Zohri se yun riwayat ki, mujh se abu-Salma ne bayan kya, unhon-ne Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se unka qaul (yani hadis ko mauqoofan naql kya) aur imam Auzai aur Muawiya bin Salam ne kaha, mujh se Zohri ne bayan kya, kaha mujh se abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aur Abdullah-bin Abdur-Rehman bin abi Husain aur Saeed bin Ziyad ne usko abu-Salma se riwayat kya, , unhon-ne Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se mauqoofan (yani abu-Saeed ka qaul (aur Abdullah-bin-Ubai Jafar ne kaha, mujh se safwaan-bin-Sulaim ne bayan kya, unhon-ne abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Abu-Ayub se, kaha maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna."
7199,"ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aap ki sunney aur itaat karne ki bait ki, khushi aur naakhushii donon haalaton mein."
7200,aur is shart par ke jo shakhs sardaarii ke laaiq hoga ( maslan Quraish mein se ho aur shara' par qaaim ho ( uski sardaarii qabool kar lengey us se jhagdaa na karein aur ye ke ham haq ko lekar khadey hongey ya haq baat kahengey jahan bhi hon aur Allah ke rastey mein malaamat karne waley ki malaamat ki parwah na karengey.
7201,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sardi mein subah ke waqt bahar nikley aur muhajireen aur Ansar khandaq khod rahe they, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey Allaah! khair to aakhirat hi ki khair hai. to Ansar w muhajireen ki maghfirat kar de.'' iska jawab logon ne diya ke ham wo hain jinhoney Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jihad par bait ki hai hamesha ke liye jab tak wo zinda hain."
7202,jab ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sunney aur itaat karne ki bait kartey to aap ham se farmatey ke jitni tumhen taqat ho.
7203,mein us waqt Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas maujood tha jab sab log Abdul-Malik bin Marwan se bait ke liye jama ho gaey. bayan kya ke unhon-ne Abdul-Malik ko likha ke ''main sunney aur itaat karne ka iqrar karta hun Abdullah Abdul-Malik ameerul-momineen ke liye Allah ke Deen aur uske rasool ki sunnat ke mutabiq jitni bhi mujh mein quwwat hogi aur ye ke mere ladkey bhi iska iqrar kartey hain.''
7204,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sunney aur itaat karne ki bait ki to aap ne mujhey iski talqeen ki ke jitni mujh mein taqat ho aur har musalman ke sath khair-khahi karne par bhi bait ki.
7205,"jab logon ne Abdul-Malik ki bait ki to Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey likha ''Allah ke bandey Abdul-Malik ameerul-momineen ke naam, main iqrar karta hun sunney aur itaat karne ki. Allah ke bandey Abdul-Malik ameerul-momineen ke liye Allah ke Deen aur uske rasool ki sunnat ke mutaabiq, jitni mujh mein taqat hogi aur mere beton ne bhi iska iqrar kya.''"
7206,maine Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha aap logon ne suleh Hudaibiya ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kis baat par bait ki thi? unhon-ne kaha ke maut par.
7207,"wo chh aadmi jinko umr (Raziallahu anhu) khilafat ke liye naamzad kar gaey they (yani Ali, Usmaan, Zubair, Talha aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ke unmein se kisi aik ko ittifaq se khaleefa bana liya jaey) ye sab jama huey aur mashwara kya. unse Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ne kaha khaleefa honey ke liye mein aap logon se koi muqaabla nahi karunga. albatta agar aap log chaahein to aap logon ke liye koi khaleefa aap hi mein se main chun dun. chunanche sab ne mil kar iska ikhtiyar Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ko de diya. jab un logon ne intikhab ki zimme-dari Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ke sipurd kar di to sab log unki taraf jhuk gaey. jitney log bhi us jamat ke peechhey chal rahe they, unmein ab maine kisi ko bhi aisa na dekha jo Abdur-Rehman ke peechhey na chal raha ho. sab log un hi ki taraf maail ho gaey aur un dinon mein unse mashwara kartey rahe jab wo raat aai jiski subah ko ham ne Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se bait ki. Miswar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya to Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) raat gaey mere yahan aaey aur darwaza khatkhataayaa yahan tak ke main bedaar ho gaya. unhon-ne kaha mera khayal hai aap so rahe they, Allah ki qism main in raaton mein bahut kam so saka hun. jaaiye ! Zuber aur Sad ko bulaaiye . main un donon buzurgon ko bula laya aur unhon-ne unse mashwara kya, phir mujhey bulaya aur kaha ke mere liye Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi bula dijiye. maine unhein bhi bulaya aur unhon-ne unse bhi sargoshii ki. yahan tak ke aadhi raat guzar gaee. phir Ali (Raziallahu anhu) unke paas khadey ho gaey aur unko apne hi liye ummeed thi. Abdur-Rehman ke dil mein bhi unki taraf se yahi dar tha, phir unhon-ne kaha ke mere liye Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi bula laaiye. main unhein bhi bula laya aur unhon-ne unse bhi sargoshi ki. aakhir subah ke muazzan ne unke darmyan judai ki. jab logon ne subah ki Namaz padh li aur ye sab log member ke paas jama huey to unhon-ne maujood muhaajireen, Ansar aur lashkaron ke qaaeydeen (leaders) ko bulaya. un logon ne us saal Haj umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath kya tha. jab sab log jama ho gaey to Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne khutba padha phir kaha ammaa ba'd! aey Ali ! maine logon ke khayalat malum kiye aur maine dekha ke wo Usman ko muqaddam samajhtey hain aur unke barabar kisi ko nahi samajhtey , isliye aap apne dil mein koi mail paida na karein. phir kaha, main aap (Usman (Raziallahu anhu)) se Allah ke Deen aur uske rasool ki sunnat aur aap ke 2 khulafaa ke tareeq ke mutabiq bait karta hun. chunanche pahley unse Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne bait ki, phir sab logon ne aur muhaajireen, Ansar aur faujiyon ke sardaaron aur tamam musalmanon ne bait ki."
7208,"ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se darakht ke nichey bait ki. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya ''Salma! kya tum bait nahi karogey ? maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! maine pehli hi martaba mein bait kar li hai, farmaya ke aur dusri martaba mein bhi kar lo.''"
7209,aik dehati ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Islam par bait ki phir usey bukhar ho gaya to usne kaha ke meri bait tod dijiye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne inkar kya phir wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kehney laga ke meri bait tod dijiye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne inkar kya aakhir wo (khud hi Madina se) chala gaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Madina bhattii ki tarah hai apni mail kuchail door kar deta hai aur saaf maal ko rakh leta hai.
7210,unhon-ne apne dada Abdullah-bin Hisham (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka zamana paya tha aur unki walida Zenab binte- Humaid unko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein lekar hazir hui thin aur arz kya tha ya Rasulullah ! us se bait ley lijiye . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye abhi kam-umr hai phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske sar par hath phera aur unke liye dua farmai aur apne tamam ghar walon ki taraf se aik hi bakri qurbaan kya kartey they.
7211,aik dehati ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Islam par bait ki phir usey Madina mein bukhar ho gaya to wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kaha ke ya Rasulullah! meri bait fasakh kar dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne inkar kya phir wo dobara aaya aur kaha ke meri bait fasakh kar dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is martaba bhi inkar kya phir wo aaya aur bait fasakh karne ka mutalba kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is martaba bhi inkar kya. iske baad wo khud hi (Madina se) chala gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke Madina bhattii ki tarah hai apni mail-kuchail ko door kar deta hai aur khalis maal rakh leta hai.
7212,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' teen aadmi aisey hain jin se Allah Taala qiyamat ke din baat nahi karega aur na unhein paak karega aur unke liye bahut sakht dukh dene wala azab hoga. aik wo shakhs jiske paas rastey mein zyada pani ho aur wo musaafir ko usmein se na pilaaey. doosra wo shakhs jo imam se bait karey aur bait ki gharaz sirf duniya kamaanaa ho agar wo imam usey kuchh duniya dedey to bait poori karey warna tod de. teesra wo shakhs jo kisi doosrey se kuchh maal Asr ke baad bech raha ho aur qism khaaey ke usey us saman ki itni-itnii qeemat mil rahi thi aur phir kharidney wala usey sachcha samajh kar us maal ko ley-ley halanke usey uski itni qeemat nahi mil rahi thii.''
7213,"ham majlis mein maujood they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' mujh se bait karo ke Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik nahi thahraaogey, chori nahi karogey, zina nahi karogey, apni aulad ko qatl nahi karogey aur apni taraf se ghad kar kisi par bohtan nahi lagaao gey aur nek kaam mein nafarmani nahi karogey. to jo koi tum mein se is waadey ko pura karey uska sawab Allah ke yahan usey milega aur jo koi un kaamon mein se kisi burey kaam ko karega uski saza usey duniya mein hi mil jaeygi to ye uske liye kaffara hoga aur jo koi unmein se kisi burai ka kaam karega aur Allah usey chipa lega to uska mamla Allah ke hawale hai. chahey to uski saza de aur chahey usey maaf kar de. ''chunaanche ham ne is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki. bait iqrar ko kehtey hain jo khaleefa Islam ke hath par hath rakh kar kya jaey ya phir kisi nek Saleh insan ke hath par ho."
7214,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aurton se zabani us aayat ke ehkaam ki bait letey ke wo Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik nahi thahraaeingii aakhir aayat tak. bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath ne kabhi kisi aurat ka hath nahi chhuwaa, siwa us aurat ke jo aap ki londi ho."
7215,"ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki to aap ne mere samney sura al-mumtahina ki ye aayat padhii (أن لا يشركن بالله شيئا‏) ye ke ''wo Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik na thahraaeingii'' aakhir tak aur hamein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nauha se mana kya phir ham mein se aik aurat ne apna hath kheench liya aur kaha ke falan aurat ne kisi nauhe mein meri madad ki thi ( mere sath mil kar nauha kya tha) aur main usey iska badla dena chahti hun. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh nahi kaha, phir wo gain aur wapas aaein ( mere sath bait karne wali aurton mein se) kisi aurat ne us bait ko pura nahi kya, siwa Umme-Sulaim aur ummul-Ulaa aur Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi abu-Sabra ki beti ke. ya abu-Sabra ki beti aur Muaz ki biwi ke aur sab aurton ne ehkaame-baia't ko poorey taur par ada na karke bait ko nahi nibhaayaa. Allah un tamam aurton ko maaf karey."
7216,"aik ganwaar ( naam naa-maaloom (ya Qais-bin abi Hazim Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya, kehney laga : ya Rasulullah ! Islam par mujh se bait lijiye . aap ne us se bait ley li, phir doosrey din bukhar mein hilhilaatey aaya kehney laga meri bait tod dijiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne inkar kya (bait nahi todii) jab wo peeth mod kar chalta hua, to farmaya Madina kya hai (lohaar ki bhattii hai) paleed aur napak (meil kuchail) ko chhaant daalta hai aur kharaa suthraa maal rakh leta hai."
7217,Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha (apne sar dard par) haaye sar phataa jata hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar tum mar jao aur main zinda raha to main tumharey liye maghfirat karunga aur tumharey liye dua karunga . Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne is par kaha afsos mera khayal hai ke aap meri maut chahtey hain aur agar aisa ho gaya to aap din ke aakhiri waqt zaroor kisi dusri aurat se shadi kar lengey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke to nahi balke main apna sar dukhney ka izhar karta hun. mera irada hua tha ke Abu-Bakar aur unke betey ko bula bhejoon aur unhein (abu-Bakar ko) khaleefa bana dun taake is par kisi dawa karne waley ya uski khahish rakhney waley ke liye koi gunjaaish na rahe lekin phir maine sochaa ke Allah khud ( kisi doosrey ko khaleefa ( nahi honey dega aur musalman bhi usey dafa' karengey. ya (aap ne is tarah farmaya ke) Allah dafa' karega aur musalman kisi aur ko khaleefa na honey dengey.
7218,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) jab zakhmi huey to unse kaha gaya ke aap apna khaleefa kisi ko kyon nahi muntakhab kar detey, aap ne farmaya ke agar kisi ko khaleefa muntakhab karta hun (to uski bhi misal hai ke) us shakhs ne apna khaleefa muntakhab kya tha jo mujh se behtar they yani Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur agar main usey musalmanon ki raey par chhorta hun to (iskii bhi misal maujood hai ke) us buzurg ne (khaleefa ka intikhab musalmanon ke liye) chhod diya tha jo mujh se behtar they yani Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) . phir logon ne aap ki tareef ki, phir unhon-ne kaha ke koi to dil se meri tareef karta hai koi dar kar. ab main to yahi ghaneemat samajhta hun ke khilafat ki zimme-daariyon mein Allah ke yahan baraabar-baraabar hi chhoot jaun, na mujhey kuchh sawab miley aur na koi azab maine khilafat ka bojh apni zindagi bhar uthaayaa. ab marney par main us baar ko nahi uthaaoonga."
7219,"unhon-ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka doosra khutba suna jab aap member par baithey huey they, ye waqia Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ke doosrey din ka hai. unhon-ne kalima shahadat padha, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khamosh they aur kuchh nahi bol rahe they, phir kaha mujhey ummeed thi ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zinda raheingey aur hamarey kaamon ki tadbeer w intizam kartey raheingey. unka mansha ye tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un sab logon ke baad tak zinda raheingey to agar aaj Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wafat pa gaey hain to Allah Taala ne tumharey samney noor (Qur'aan) ko baqi rakha hai jiske zariey tum hidayat hasil kartey rahogey aur Allah ne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us se hidayat ki aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathi (jo ghaare-saur mein) 2 mein ke doosrey hain, bila shak wo tumharey khilafat ke maamlon ke liye tamam musalmanon mein sabse behtar hain, to utho aur unse bait karo. aik jamat unse pahley hi Saqeefa bani saaida mein bait kar chuki thi, phir aam logon ne member par bait ki. Zohri ne bayan kya, unse Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne, unhon-ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke wo Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se, us din keh rahe they, member par chadh aaiye. chunanche wo iska barabar israar kartey rahe, yahan tak ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) member par chadh gaey aur sab logon ne aap se bait ki."
7220,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik khatun aaiin aur kisi maamle mein aap se guftgu ki, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse kaha ke wo dobara aap ke paas aaiin. unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! agar main aaoon aur aapko na paon to phir aap kya farmatey hain? jaisey unka ishara wafat ki taraf ho. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar mujhey na paogey to Abu-Bakar ke paas aaiyo."
7221,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne qabaayel Buzaakhaa ke wafad se (jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ke baad murtad ho gaya tha aur ab maafi ke liye aaya tha) farmaya ke oonton ki dumon ke peechhey-peechhey jangalon mein ghoomtey raho, yahan tak ke Allah Taala apne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke khaleefa aur muhajireen ko koi baat batla de jiski wjah se wo tumhara qasoor maaf kar dein."
7222,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) meri ummat mein) baara ameer hongey, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne koi aisi baat farmai jo maine nahi suni , baad mein mere walid ne bataya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya ke wo sab ke sab Quraish khandan se hongey."
7223,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) meri ummat mein) baara ameer hongey, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne koi aisi baat farmai jo maine nahi suni , baad mein mere walid ne bataya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya ke wo sab ke sab Quraish khandan se hongey."
7224,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai! mera irada hua ke main lakdiyon ke jama karne ka hukm dun, phir Namaz ke liye azan dene ka, phir kisi se kahun ke wo logon ko Namaz padhaaey aur main iske bajaey un logon ke paas jaun (jo jamat mein Sharik nahi hotey) aur unhein unke gharon samet jalaa dun. qism hai us zaat ki jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ke tum se kisi ko agar ye ummeed ho ke wahan motii haddi ya 2 ( مرماة حسنتين ( bakri ke khur ke darmyan ka gosht milega to wo zaroor (namaz ( isha mein Sharik ho."
7225,"Abdullah-bin Ka'b-bin-Maalik, Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke naa-beenaa ho janey ke zamaney mein unke sab ladkon mein yahi rastey mein unke sath chaltey they, (unhon) ne bayan kya ke maine Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha ke jab wo jange-Tabook mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nahi ja saktey they, phir unhon-ne apna pura waqia bayan kya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne musalmanon ko ham se guftgu karne se rok diya tha to ham pachaas din usi haalat mein rahe, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne elaan kya ke Allah ne hamari tauba qabool kar li hai."
